pub fn judge_cast(
    &self,
    ty1: &Type,
    ty2: &Type,
    base_differs: bool,
    loc: &Loc,
    constrs: &mut Option<&mut Constrs>
) -> Result<bool, String>

Judges whether ty1 can be cast as ty2 at the location. If base_differs is true, base types do not have the subtype relation each other. stack is internally used for avoiding infinite loop.
